---
title: Baked Chicken Parmigiana with Oven-Baked Fries
description: Why go out for this nostalgic pub classic when you can create it right in your own kitchen? There’s not much to analyse here – just
good old-fashioned tasty, gooey chicken parmy. This one's going straight to the trophy room!

